## 6. Controller Codes

### `app/controllers/users_controller.rb`

```ruby
class UsersController < ApplicationController
  def index
    @users = User.includes(:posts, :comments).order(:created_at)
  end
end
```

### `app/controllers/posts_controller.rb`

```ruby
class PostsController < ApplicationController
  def index
    @posts = Post.includes(:user, :category).order(:created_at)
  end
end
```

### `app/controllers/categories_controller.rb`

```ruby
class CategoriesController < ApplicationController
  def index
    @categories = Category.includes(:posts).order(:created_at)
  end
end
```

### `app/controllers/comments_controller.rb`

```ruby
class CommentsController < ApplicationController
  def index
    @comments = Comment.includes(:user, :post).order(:created_at)
